! Title: Flixbaba + Lanky-Bar Safe Filter
! Description: Blocks lanky-bar.com popups/scripts on flixbaba.tv and ensures vidsrc.net videos play smoothly
! Last updated: 2025-08-20
! Homepage: https://github.com/MattWMCP/adguard-filters

! --- Block lanky-bar scripts precisely on flixbaba ---
||lanky-bar.com/ciDR9.*$script,domain=flixbaba.tv
flixbaba.tv##script:has-text(lanky-bar)
flixbaba.tv##a[href*="lanky-bar"]
flixbaba.tv##iframe[src*="lanky-bar"]
flixbaba.tv##+js(nowoif, lanky-bar)
flixbaba.tv##+js(nostif, lanky-bar)

! --- Whitelist video provider to prevent buffering ---
@@||vidsrc.net^$document,domain=flixbaba.tv

! --- Optional: future safe additions can go below ---
